      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 2.8 - 老子 2.9</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 2.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>高下相傾，音聲相和，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>that (the ideas of) height and lowness arise from the contrast of the one with the other;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-002__align-007">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-002</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 2.10 - 老子 2.11</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 2.7 - 老子 2.8</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>前後相隨。是以聖人處無為之事，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>that the musical notes and tones become harmonious through the relation of one with another; and that being before and behind give the idea of one following another.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-002__align-008">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-002</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 2.12 - 老子 2.13</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 2.9 - 老子 2.10</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>行不言之教；萬物作焉而不辭，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Therefore the sage manages affairs without doing anything, and conveys his instructions without the use of speech. All things spring up, and there is not one which declines to show itself;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-002__align-009">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-002</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
